Description: AZ Pool Arena Scoreboard - Kiosk Application
 Full-screen kiosk scoreboard application for billiards/pool arenas.
 Features real-time scoring, camera streaming with delay, DVR recording,
 tournament brackets, and menu ordering integration.
 .
 After installation, the machine will auto-boot into kiosk mode
 displaying the scoreboard application in full-screen.
